sect1.para:
Let us assume that there is a user &obsuser1;
who has created a package &obshome1;/&gitproject;
on &obsa;. Now, a second user, &obsuser2;,
would like to submit a code change request to that package.

step.para:
This creates a branched package in &obsa; at &obsbranch2;/&gitproject;
     and checks out a directory
     &obsworkdir2;:branches:home:&obsuser1;:&gitproject;.
